Unlike the previous revision, this one is complete and, except for the two "Tales" graphic novel specials, digitally re-coloured and ripped in hi-res throughout. However, the design of the new editions on which the original rips are based is, IMHO, amazingly ugly (in digital format, anyway), so I used the far lovelier covers of the old editions instead and threw out as much extraneous material as possible
